Author: Jochen Voss <voss@debian.org>
Bug-Debian: http://bugs.debian.org/205367
---
diff --git a/src/MAKEFLOPPIES b/src/MAKEFLOPPIES
index 91fad1e..c8cdb43 100755
--- a/src/MAKEFLOPPIES
+++ b/src/MAKEFLOPPIES
